OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774289156
OL,3,CKeely Hodgkinson wins historic 800m
OL,4,Ctitle at World Indoors
OL,6,FKeely Hodgkinson lived up to her own
OL,7,Fpromise of "domination" as she led an
OL,8,Fhistoric gold-medal sweep for Great
OL,9,FBritain at the World Indoor
OL,10,FChampionships in Poland.
OL,12,FHodgkinson secured the 800m title in a
OL,13,Fchampionship record time of 1:55.30,
OL,14,Fmarking a triumphant return to the
OL,15,Fvenue in Torun where she won her first
OL,16,Fsenior title five years ago.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
