PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774289156
OL,3,CKeely Hodgkinson wins historic 800m
OL,4,Ctitle at World Indoors
OL,6,FThe 24-year-old's victory sparked an
OL,7,Fincredible 30-minute blitz for the
OL,8,FBritish team, as training partner
OL,9,FGeorgia Hunter Bell and pole vaulter
OL,10,FMolly Caudery both secured world
OL,11,Ftitles of their own.
OL,13,FHodgkinson, who set a new world indoor
OL,14,Frecord just last month, took control
OL,15,Fearly on, beating Swiss silver
OL,16,Fmedallist Audrey Werro by a massive
OL,17,F1.34 seconds, proving her fitness
OL,18,Fafter an injury-plagued 2025 season.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774289156
OL,3,CKeely Hodgkinson wins historic 800m
OL,4,Ctitle at World Indoors
OL,6,F"I think my word this year has been
OL,7,Fdomination," Hodgkinson said after the
OL,8,Fhistoric win. "When I'm in the shape
OL,9,Fof my life, why leave it to chance? If
OL,10,Fyou're going to beat me, I'll make you
OL,11,Fwork hard for it."
OL,13,FHodgkinson, from Atherton, then
OL,14,Freturned to the track later to run the
OL,15,Fanchor leg in the women's 4x400m relay
OL,16,Ffinal ` part of an experimental
OL,17,Fquartet which also featured surprise
OL,18,Faddition Dina Asher-Smith.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774289156
OL,3,CKeely Hodgkinson wins historic 800m
OL,4,Ctitle at World Indoors
OL,6,FHer 50.1s split was, incredibly, the
OL,7,Ffastest leg in a final that started
OL,8,Fless than an hour after she crossed
OL,9,Fthe line in the 800m.
OL,11,FIt also prevented her from seeing
OL,12,FHunter Bell capture her first world
OL,13,Ftitle, on a night Hodgkinson felt the
OL,14,FBritish women "absolutely smashed it".
OL,16,FHunter Bell, the world 800m silver and
OL,17,FOlympic 1500m bronze medallist, was in
OL,18,Ffine tactical form, leading the pack
OL,19,Fthat reeled in Ethiopian Birke Haylom
OL,20,Fbefore crossing the line in 3:58.53.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774289156
OL,3,CKeely Hodgkinson wins historic 800m
OL,4,Ctitle at World Indoors
OL,6,FIt was another remarkable achievement
OL,7,Fthe 32-year-old Hunter Bell can add to
OL,8,Fa CV which as recently as 2024 would
OL,9,Fhave listed a very different current
OL,10,Femployer.
OL,12,FThe once prodigious junior athlete
OL,13,Freturned to running during the Covid-
OL,14,F19 pandemic, eventually reuniting with
OL,15,Fformer coach Trevor Painter.
OL,17,F"This time two years ago I was working
OL,18,Fin tax sales and now I'm the world
OL,19,Fchampion," she said. "Nothing is set
OL,20,Fin stone and you can really go for
OL,21,Fanything."
OL,26,@{D@JO]{D@VOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
