PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1774289156
OL,3,CKeely Hodgkinson wins historic 800m
OL,4,Ctitle at World Indoors
OL,6,FCaudery was the only woman to clear
OL,7,F4.85m in the pole vault, breaking what
OL,8,Fhad felt like a curse after a shock
OL,9,Fqualifying exit at the Paris Olympics
OL,10,Fin 2024 and an ankle injury in the
OL,11,Fwarm-up at 2025's World Championships.
OL,13,FShe said: "Six weeks ago, I couldn't
OL,14,Fget off the ground and I was in a dark
OL,15,Fplace. Today to come here and do this
OL,16,Fmeans more than anyone knows, after
OL,17,FParis and after Tokyo and after last
OL,18,Fyear it's just a relief.
OL,20,F"It felt so good, I haven't enjoyed
OL,21,Fjumping so much in such a long time."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
